        {
            "title": "黑期跌117點  ADR低水144點   阿里巴巴跌網易升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期跌118點或0.51%，報23272。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨天收市低水144點或0.62%，報23308點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250116_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數滑落2.37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)收入稍遜預期，美國存託證券(ADS)股價下挫7.6%，較本港低6.2%，報120.89元 ; 網易(09999)績後獲看好，ADR升14.6%，較香港收市價高水14%，折合191.69港元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京東(09618) ADR較香港收市價低水1%，折合134.02港元 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣516.42元，較港收市價較港收市價低0.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報91.81元，較香港收市價高1.3% ; 港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣375.06元，較香港收市價低0.6% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣65.59元，較香港收市價低0.4%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪(01211) ADR較香港收市價低水0.6%，折合417,87港元 ; 理想汽車(02015) ADR較香港收市價高水0.1%，折合111.43港元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14933093-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c117%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4144%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e8%b7%8c%e7%b6%b2%e6%98%93%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/HK-STOCK_ADR-1_source-bp_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 08:55:59",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
